```r
allDf %>%
  group_by(index) %>%
  filter(rel_ab == max(rel_ab,
                       na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
  dplyr::select(index,genus) %>%
  rename(most.ab = genus) %>%
  left_join(sinspuBrayPCoAMeta,.,
            by = \index\") -> sinspuBrayPCoAMeta
